-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 汽车内饰清洁美容的必要性</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 汽车内饰中的地毯、座椅、空调风口、行李箱等处，很容易积存一些灰尘沙粒，不仅会有异味，而且在潮湿的环境下也很容易滋生出细菌，威胁到车主的健康。内饰清洗的必要性</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">车内是一个密闭空间，车内的空气不容易与外界流通更换，尤其春夏天风沙天气，车内经常会积存一些沙粒，严重影响人员乘坐的舒适性。在春夏季呼吸道疾病多发时期，容易增加车内人员的患病几率，甚至增加乘车者之间病菌交互传染的可能性，尤其对于易感人群，汽车内饰清洁是非常必要的。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">汽车的内室空间比较狭小<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>由于车门的开关、人员的进出、抽烟、喝酒或吃一些食物所留下的残渣会引起大量的螨虫、细菌的滋长，还会产生一些刺激性的味道；</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"><img src=\"http://qyw115131.chinaw3.com/data/files/mall/article/201406090920323438.jpg\" alt=\"shinei1.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 内饰清洗的作用</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">汽车内饰清洁有助于延长使用寿命：车室的清洁、杀菌、除臭，可以有效地防止各种污物对车室如地毯、真皮座椅、纤维织物等的腐蚀，同时专业汽车美容店还有专业的内饰保养上光剂保护内饰各个部件；</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">创造良好车内环境保护健康：汽车内饰中的地毯、座椅、空调风口、行李箱等处<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>经常接触潮湿的空气或水渍，在特定的环境中，这些地方最易令细菌滋生，使内饰霉变，散发出臭气，不但影响了室内空气环境，更重要的是对您的健康发出了威胁。汽车内饰清洁美容能够帮助车主做好清洁工作，同时起到保养汽车内饰防止内饰部件过早老化的作用。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"><img src=\"http://qyw115131.chinaw3.com/data/files/mall/article/201406090920339274.jpg\" alt=\"shinei2.jpg\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 购买并关注赛浪旧宫店微信就可获赠深度室内空气净化组合（甲醛清除、臭氧杀菌、空调风道清洗、室内桑拿）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"><img src=\"http://qyw