di-language: AR-SA;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 免费洗车卡</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"><img src=\"http://qyw115131.chinaw3.com/data/files/mall/article/201406091010057493.JPG\" alt=\"赠洗车卡.JPG\" /><br /></span></p>',255,1,1402308665),(14,'','空运过来的美食湖北家乡菜—柿红院',7,0,'','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">柿红院是制售湖北老家土菜的南方私房菜餐馆，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span>年在北京金融街的一个四合院开店，因院中有一棵柿树而起名柿红院。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 20.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">柿红院菜品特点：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 20.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">、食材优质：所有食材都是在老家基地有机种植和野生放养，不打农药，不施化肥，不盖大棚，自然生长，按季节吃菜，每星期定点通过航空和大巴快运到北京。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 20.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">、做工考究：柿红院做菜讲究慢火细工，烹饪方法多采用烧、烩、闷、蒸、煎等，不像一般餐馆急火速成。客人进餐都是提前预定，每天限量，这样给厨师留够充足的备料、制作时间，做到土菜精做，粗菜细作。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 20.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">、家味浓厚：&ldquo;吃老家土菜，找家里感觉&rdquo;是柿红院的经营理念，因此，柿红院菜品烹饪全部采用老家传统方法和老家佐料制作，味道地道、纯正，让客人一看到菜肴就倍感亲切，就像回到了家里，吃奶奶做的菜，吃外婆做的菜，吃妈妈做的菜。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 20.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">、土菜齐全：柿红院厨师全是老家人，菜品以老家土菜、特菜为主，突出湖北、湖南特色，品种齐全，花样繁多，许多菜都是几十年前儿时吃的、上不了桌面的菜。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 20.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\">、健康烹饪：烹饪菜品，柿红院坚持&ldquo;三低&rdquo;原则（低盐、低油、低糖）少放鸡精、味精，煲汤、茶饮等采用矿泉水。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">柿红院进餐实行预定配菜制，每天<span lang=\"EN-US\">3-5</span>桌，消费标准<span lang=\"EN-US\">200-500</span>元<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>人。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 特色蔬菜介绍：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme